     >rahmen  up?
     if   x1 y3 1- x4 DefUnten 1 scrollup  
          DefUnten x1 over .|  x4 swap .|  
     else x1 y3 x4 DefUnten 1 scrolldn  x1 y3 .|  x4 y3 .|  
     then y3 up? if 1- else 1+ then is y3  normal
     y3 1- istUnten ComFenster  
